OL,3,CGovernment unveils 'bus revolution' to
OL,4,Cgive local authorities more control
OL,6,FLocal authorities will be able to take
OL,7,Fcontrol of their own bus services,
OL,8,Funder new government plans.
OL,10,FTransport Secretary Louise Haigh
OL,11,Fclaimed her "bus revolution" will save
OL,12,Fvital routes nationwide.
OL,14,FLegislation which gives all local
OL,15,Ftransport authorities new powers to
OL,16,Frun their own bus services will be
OL,17,Flaid before Parliament on Monday in
OL,18,Fthe form of a statutory instrument.
