OL,3,CGovernment unveils 'bus revolution' to
OL,4,Cgive local authorities more control
OL,6,FOnly metro mayors, like Greater
OL,7,FManchester's Andy Burnham, can
OL,8,Fcurrently control services.
OL,10,FThe government has also initiated a
OL,11,Fconsultation on simplified guidance to
OL,12,Fspeed up processes and reduce costs
OL,13,Ffor local leaders looking to bring
OL,14,Fservices under public control.
