OL,3,CGovernment unveils 'bus revolution' to
OL,4,Cgive local authorities more control
OL,6,FThe annual total distance travelled by
OL,7,Fbuses in England has fallen by nearly
OL,8,F300 million miles since 2010,
OL,9,Faccording to the department.
OL,11,FMs Haigh said: "Buses are the
OL,12,Flifeblood of our communities, but for
OL,13,Ftoo many people it has become
OL,14,Fimpossible to rely on local services,
OL,15,Fas routes have been slashed and
OL,16,Ftimetables hollowed out.
OL,18,F"Today is the first stop on our
OL,19,Fjourney to delivering better buses
OL,20,Facross the country.
