OL,3,CGovernment unveils 'bus revolution' to
OL,4,Cgive local authorities more control
OL,6,F"After decades of failed deregulation,
OL,7,Flocal leaders will finally have the
OL,8,Fpowers to provide services that
OL,9,Fdeliver for passengers.
OL,11,F"And we are taking steps to support
OL,12,Flocal leaders to deliver improved bus
OL,13,Fservices faster and cheaper than ever
OL,14,Fbefore.
OL,16,F"With local communities firmly back in
OL,17,Fthe driving seat, our bus revolution
OL,18,Fwill save vital routes up and down the
OL,19,Fcountry and put passengers first."
