OL,6,F"Whilst franchising may not be
OL,7,Fsuitable for all areas, everyone
OL,8,Fshould have access to a quality bus
OL,9,Fservice without risk of it being cut,
OL,10,Fwhich is why we are also calling for a
OL,11,Fminimum service level guarantee and
OL,12,Flong-term, ringfenced funding for all
OL,13,Flocal authorities."
